title: Ahead of Market: 10 things that will decide stock market action on Friday
description: Indian markets ended slightly higher as IT stocks gained ahead of the RBI policy decision. Mixed global cues, a weak rupee and FII outflows capped gains, while analysts warned of resistance near 26,150 and possible volatility on Friday.
